name: Analog Chorus
details:
The Joyo JF-37 Analog Chorus pedal uses an BBD chip to give you the classic analog chorus sound and accurate reproduction.
Analog Chorus can expand your musical horizon, when it comes to original tones.
Rate and Depth knobs let you adjust chorus speed and depth.
True bypass design is used to minimise tone loss.
Simple design and a sturdy casing.
